":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T18:57:42.000Z","msg":"我個仔今年小六，已經決定左送佢入董之英磨練下，將來做個男子漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:18:28.000Z","msg":"張振興有振興男兒<br />\n我地有董事男兒<br />\n<br />\n有朝一日你個仔會有我地嘅成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ab0c40453c1018e84715dfd90f2bd0cb2ac8e4","tid":999462,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:27:30.000Z","msg":"【校園欺凌】第3條欺凌片流出！董之英中學1男生被同學蒙頭壓騎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/999543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/999543</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d449aa76054da7196b5f06ab44173d875528b8de","tid":999462,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"我校全人教育又贏一仗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}